{"tid":1088694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又係撞車黨？怪男瞓地擋車　仲識彈起出重拳？","createTime":"2019-04-02T08:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T08:59:34.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26b6c97fe0f90bb6dd1625e174a361e68743b197","tid":1088694,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:36:31.000Z","msg":"又係撞車黨？怪男瞓地擋車 仲識彈起出重拳？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HUOAMf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HUOAMf&d=mFE05qKCD2WHpL72sA8m6w1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=4153712b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HUOAMf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190402/photo/bkn-20190402153714576-0402_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190402155503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190402%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190402153714576-0402_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190402155503&h=9ca8a344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咩事咁激動？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撞車黨現身中環？近日有男子以奇怪姿勢躺在馬路，以身擋車，又突然彈起「重拳出擊」，拍打路過貨Van的車頭玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」的片段所見，上周五（29日）上午在中環荷李活道近安樂樓，有男子橫躺在一輛貨Van前，阻擋貨Van駛離。<br />\n<br />\n該男子在車前蹺腳輾轉，又一度交叉雙手墊起頭部。未幾他忽然跳起，揮拳擊向車頭玻璃。有目擊者指，該男子不停指罵貨Van司機︰「行到好遠都仲聽到佢大嗌『落車呀XX』」。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛戲謔謂︰「懂得起身拍打大銀幕，已經可以告他」、「導演一日未嗌Cut，千祈都唔好停」、「突然回光返照」。有人則教路︰「最好就關窗坐喺度，唔好開車，唔好落車，有手機就拎出嚟影，證據緊要」。"},{"pid":"8a49b5b87eab246a25f50498dd7d7115bada3d75","tid":1088694,"uid":13288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6KNHydf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6KNHydf.png&h=89fdd64e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f9fdba239875c006027ec24b2c86cc92cf5568e","tid":1088694,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"白卡廢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那專材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}